videos.description: The Suns' Mikal Bridges leaves the game after he drives to the basket against LeBron James and falls down awkwardly after making the layup.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Bridges shaken up after awkard fall on layup attempt) 2020/12/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bridges shaken up after awkard fall on layup attempt

videos.description: Talen Horton-Tucker crosses over to freeze a defender and glides through the lane to put in a finesse layup around DeAndre Ayton.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Horton-Tucker weaves through defenders for difficult layup) 2020/12/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: Horton-Tucker weaves through defenders for difficult layup

videos.description: Anthony Davis drives hard to the basket and readjusts awkwardly around Damian Jones to somehow bank in an and-1 layup.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (AD finesses awkward and-1 layup around Jones) 2020/12/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: AD finesses awkward and-1 layup around Jones

videos.description: Anthony Davis cuts the Suns' lead to 92-91 as he drains a sweet step-back 3-pointer in the face of Jalen Smith to end the third quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Davis splashes step-back 3-pointer to end the 3rd quarter) 2020/12/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Davis splashes step-back 3-pointer to end the 3rd quarter

videos.description: Devin Booker breezes by the Lakers defense and glides to the rack to stuff down an uncontested two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Booker soars for 2-handed stuff

videos.description: Anthony Davis scores 35 points on 11-of-16 shooting from the field and 6-of-7 shooting from 3-point land as he leads the Lakers to a 114-113 win over the Suns in their final preseason game.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Highlight (AD racks up 35 points in Lakers' preseason win vs. Suns) 2020/12/18 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: AD racks up 35 points in Lakers' preseason win vs. Suns
